channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: BYU Cougars Unveil 1996 Throwback Football Uniforms
item.description: As part of its 100th season celebration, BYU has unveiled 1996 throwback uniforms that will be worn in the Big XII opener against Kansas State on Sept. 21.

item.title: New York Mets Honor Willie Mays, Jerry Grote With Jersey Patches
item.description: The New York Mets will honor the lives of former players Willie Mays and Jerry Grote by wearing memorial patches on their jerseys for the remainder of the season.

item.title: Philadelphia Eagles To Wear Kelly Green Throwback Uniforms Twice In 2024
item.description: The Philadelphia Eagles will wear their Kelly green throwback uniforms twice this season, including against the Jacksonville Jaguars on Nov. 3 and Dallas Cowboys on Dec. 29.
